MYSQL TABLES
============

user
openid

bid
rate
currency
account -- associative table. links users and their openids.
funds

top - cache



CONTROLLERS
===========

user
	index - see my profie
	settings - change things in my profile
	view - view someone's profile
	link - add a new linked profile
	login
	logout

bids
	index - see active bids
	my - see my active bids
	history - see my inactive bids
	put - put a bid
	cancel - cancel a bid
	accept - accept a bid
	
top
	index - see top 100
	? place - see my place in the top
